title: The Baker Mayfield Rumor, Tom Brady's Next Deal, and the QB Landscape | GM Street (Ep. 263)
description:
The Ringer’s Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier sit down to vent about the 76ers (02:00) before discussing the rumor about the Patriots trying to trade up for Baker Mayfield (06:00), Tom Brady's two-year plan (11:00), how Matt Ryan's contract changes the league (13:30), first impressions of Lamar Jackson (20:00), the quarterback situation in Philadelphia (25:30), and Jason Witten's retirement (33:15).
